desc: Celly's is the only Distribution company bringing Health Extension to Canada. Health Extension is a grain-inclusive dry dog food using a moderate amount of named meat meals as its main source of animal protein. Celly's also Distributes the Snugarooz brand. a high quality pet toys made from recycled water bottles.
